@startuml C1_Manage_Storage_Areas_Process_View
title C1 – Manage Storage Areas (Process View)

actor "Port Authority Officer" as Officer
participant "StorageAreasController\n(API Layer)" as Controller
participant "StorageAreaMapper\n(Data Mapper)" as Mapper
participant "PortContext\n(EF Core)" as Context
database "Database\n(SQL / InMemory)" as DB

Officer -> Controller : POST /api/StorageAreas\n(CreateStorageAreaDTO)
Controller -> Mapper : Converte DTO → Entidade de Domínio
Mapper --> Controller : Retorna objeto StorageArea

Controller -> Context : Adiciona entidade StorageArea
Context -> DB : Persiste dados (SaveChanges)
DB --> Context : Confirma inserção
Context --> Controller : OK

Controller --> Officer : HTTP 201 Created\n(StorageAreaDTO)

@enduml
